      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·011.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">般.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>於皇時周，陟其高山。嶞山喬嶽，允猶翕河。
敷天之下，裒時之對，時周之命。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Oh! great now is Kâu.
We ascend the high hills,
Both those that are long and narrow, and the lofty mountains.
Yes, and (we travel) along the regulated Ho,
All under the sky,
Assembling those who now respond to me.
Thus it is that the appointment belongs to Kâu.</seg>
      </tuv>
